    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-label">Average velocity</div>
      <p>By the FTC, \(P'(t)=\ln(t^2+1)\), so average velocity on \([1,5]\) is:</p>
      <div class="math-display">
        \[a = \frac{P(5)-P(1)}{5-1} = \frac{1}{4}\int_1^5\ln(u^2+1)\,du \approx \frac{9.107}{4} \approx 2.277\]
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-label">Speed at t = 3</div>
      <p>Speed equals \(|P'(3)|=|\ln(3^2+1)|=\ln(10)\approx 2.303\).</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-label">Compute the ratio</div>
      <div class="math-display">
        \[\frac{a}{b} = \frac{2.277}{2.303} \approx 0.953\]
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="key-insight">Answer: <strong>(C) 0.953</strong>.</div>
